Definition: a chemical reaction in which water reacts with a compound to produce other compounds
Example: involves the splitting of a bond and the addition of the hydrogen cation and the hydroxide anion from the water
Synonyms: verb, change, hydrolize, hydrolise, chemical_reaction, a, chemical, reaction, in, which, water, reacts, with, compound, to, produce, other, compounds, involves, the, splitting, of, bond, and, addition, hydrogen, cation, hydroxide, anion, from
Category: noun.process
